      <p begin="00:10.400" end="00:12.150" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:10.400" end="00:10.550">Your</span> <span begin="00:10.670" end="00:10.900">da</span><span begin="00:10.900" end="00:11.000">ta</span> <span begin="00:11.060" end="00:11.210">cen</span><span begin="00:11.210" end="00:11.340">ters</span> <span begin="00:11.340" end="00:11.540">I'm</span> <span begin="00:11.540" end="00:11.750">bree</span><span begin="00:11.750" end="00:11.950">zing</span> <span begin="00:11.950" end="00:12.150">through</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你的数据中心我穿梭自如</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你的數據中心我穿梭自如</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あんたのデータセンターなんて楽勝よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 데이터 센터쯤은 가볍게 뚫어버리지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je traverse tes centres de données avec aisance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me paseo por tus centros de datos como si nada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Deine Rechenzentren durchstreife ich mit Leichtigkeit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pelos seus data centers eu passo voando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Твои дата-центры я пролетаю с ветерком</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Attraverso i vostri data center in un soffio</span></p>
