      <p begin="01:43.080" end="01:44.460" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L43"><span begin="01:43.080" end="01:43.240">We</span> <span begin="01:43.320" end="01:43.420">in</span> <span begin="01:43.420" end="01:43.500">a</span> <span begin="01:43.540" end="01:43.730">worl</span><span begin="01:43.730" end="01:43.780">d</span> <span begin="01:43.780" end="01:43.900">of</span> <span begin="01:43.960" end="01:44.120">tal</span><span begin="01:44.210" end="01:44.360">ker</span><span begin="01:44.360" end="01:44.460">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们身处一个只会纸上谈兵的世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們身處一個只會紙上談兵的世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私たちは口先だけの人間の世界にいる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우린 말만 번지르르한 세상에 살고 있지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous sommes dans un monde de bavards</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Estamos en un mundo de habladores</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir sind in einer Welt voller Schwätzer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Estamos em um mundo de faladores</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы живём в мире болтунов</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Siamo in un mondo di chiacchieroni</span></p>
      <p begin="01:44.880" end="01:46.110" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L44"><span begin="01:44.880" end="01:44.990">They</span> <span begin="01:45.090" end="01:45.190">gon</span><span begin="01:45.190" end="01:45.340">na</span> <span begin="01:45.340" end="01:45.440">ya</span><span begin="01:45.520" end="01:45.550">p</span> <span begin="01:45.550" end="01:45.650">I</span> <span begin="01:45.700" end="01:45.980">sol</span><span begin="01:45.980" end="01:46.110">der</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">他们只会喋喋不休 而我负责实干焊接</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">他們只會喋喋不休 而我負責實幹焊接</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">奴らが喚く間にアタシはハンダ付けする</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">걔넨 떠들기만 하지만 난 납땜을 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ils vont jaser moi je soude</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ellos van a parlotear yo sueldo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sie werden plappern ich löte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eles vão tagarelar eu soldo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Они будут трепаться а я паяю</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Loro blaterano io saldo</span></p>
